policies.policy_text: Abweichend von den oben genannten Zahlungsmodalitäten erfolgt die Bezahlung per Rechnungstellung an die jeweilige Gesellschaft. Die Vorlage einer Kreditkarte ist bei geschäftlichen Anmietungen nicht erforderlich. Alle Mietfahrzeuge werden automatisch zum gewählten Firmensitz zugestellt und ebenso dort abgeholt.

rental_checklists: Be sure to bring your valid documents and means of payment:
*Debit card customers are required to provide two proofs of identification and/or residence (e.g. utility bill and bank statement), and may be required to provide additional information

key_facts_policies.policy_text: DOCUMENTATION- ALL DRIVERS MUST PRODUCE ALL PARTS OF A VALID DRIVING LICENCE. NON-EU LICENCE HOLDERS ARE REQUIRED TO HAVE AN INTERNATIONAL DRIVING PERMIT IF THE LICENCE IS NOT IN ENGLISH. INTERNATIONAL TRAVELLERS MUST PRODUCE A PASSPORT, PROOF OF RETURN TRAVEL AND RESIDENCY INFORMATION WHILE IN IRELAND. DOMESTIC RENTERS MUST PRODUCE PHOTO ID – PASSPORT OR DRIVING LICENCE. FOR ALL DRIVERS, WE RESERVE THE RIGHT TO REQUEST ADDITIONAL ID OR CONDUCT FURTHER ID CHECKS. THESE MAY INCLUDE ID CHECKS WITH EXTERNAL PARTNERS WHO MAY VERIFY SUPPLIED DETAILS AGAINST DATABASES TO WHICH THEY HAVE ACCESS.

Abweichend von den oben genannten Zahlungsmodalitäten erfolgt die Bezahlung per Rechnungstellung an die jeweilige Gesellschaft. Die Vorlage einer Kreditkarte ist bei geschäftlichen Anmietungen nicht erforderlich. Alle Mietfahrzeuge werden automatisch zum gewählten Firmensitz zugestellt und ebenso dort abgeholt.
If you wish to discuss or dispute any matters concerning damage to your rental vehicle then please contact the Rental Company using the contact information below: eva.gjeli@ehiglobal.com

Airport locations do not accept debit cards.  All renters must pay a deposit of 250 EUR using a major credit card which is in their own name and if the rental has not been prepaid, the estimated full rental charges.

ENTERPRISE RENT-A-CAR PROVIDES DAMAGE WAIVER -DW- WHICH REDUCES THE COSTS ASSOCIATED WITH DAMAGE TO AND-OR THEFT OF THE ENTERPRISE VEHICLE SUBJECT TO THE TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF YOUR RENTAL AGREEMENT. DAMAGE AND THEFT RESPONSIBILITY IS THE FULL VALUE OF THE VEHICLE. DAMAGE WAIVER MAY BE MANDATORY AND INCLUDED IN THE QUOTE. CUSTOMERS WHO CAN PROVIDE INDEPENDENT AND VERIFIED PROVISION TO COVER DAMAGE AND THEFT TO THE ENTERPRISE VEHICLE MAY BE ABLE TO DECLINE DW. THE DW AMOUNT FOR THIS BRANCH IS 17.62 EUROS PLUS VAT PER DAY.
ALL DRIVERS MUST HAVE BEEN ELIGIBLE TO HOLD A LICENCE FOR EIGHT YEARS FOR A-F CLASS VEHICLES, 11 YEARS FOR MPVS AND VANS AND 13 YEARS FOR SMALL PREMIUMS.
